reviewText: Hopefully one day someone will digitally remaster this film.

Barbie Benton is the reason I got this movie and I wasn't disappointed and that about covers the movie. Acting was so bad I watched most of it in fast forward actually that made it better. Remember this movie was made in the late 60's early 70's and a playboy film with the worst music I have ever heard as a youngster at the time I never listened to any of that garbage it was just madeup stuff. But back then that's how it was and I guess we liked it altho now I would rather have my teeth pulled. But if you remember Barbie Benton it's worth the watch it was here only movie and you will see why besides naked that's all the talent she had
I love how Barbie came off in the story as she gained the smarts needed to deal with "Johns" as the movie went on. Just a hometown girl who made it big using her brains.
